@deffn {Fun@,{c}@~ao} summand_to_rec (@var{summand}, @var{k}, @var{n})
@deffnx {Fun@,{c}@~ao} summand_to_rec (@var{summand}, [@var{k}, @var{lo}, @var{hi}], @var{n})

Retorna a recorr@^encia satisfeita pelo somat@'orio

@example
     sup
    ====
    \
     >     x
    /
    ====
  k = inf
